text: Okeechobee County is a county in the U.S. state of Florida, and was formed on May 8, 1917. As of 2020, 39,644 people lived there. Okeechobee County's seat is Okeechobee. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official county website Category:Florida counties Category:1917 establishments in the United States Category:1910s establishments in Florida
